	//		Array of Strings representing order to try corners in, like ["TR", "BL"].
	//		Possible values are:
	//			* "BL" - bottom left
	//			* "BR" - bottom right
	//			* "TL" - top left
	//			* "TR" - top right
	//	padding:
	//		set padding to put some buffer around the element you want to position.
	// example:
	//		Try to place node's top right corner at (10,20).
